ace	stoneroot	storksbill	strangler	strawberry	strawflower	streptocarpus	stringybark	strophanthus	styrax	subshrub	succory	succulent	suffrutex	sugar-bush	sugarberry	sugarcane	sugi	suksdorfia	sulla	sumac	sumach	sunberry	sundew	sundrops	sunflower	sunray	sunrose	swallowwort	swan-flower	swan-neck	swanflower	swanneck	swede	sweetbriar	sweetbrier	sweetleaf	sweetpea	sweetsop	switch-ivy	sycamore	syringa	tacamahac	tagasaste	tail-flower	tailflower	tailwort	talipot	tall-grass	tallgrass	tamarack	tamarillo	tamarind	tamarindo	tamarisk	tanekaha	tangelo	tangerine	tanglebush	tangor	tannia	tansy	tar-wood	tare	taro	tarragon	tarweed	tarwood	tea	teaberry	teak	teasel	teasle	teazel	teff	tendergreen	terebinth	tetterwort	thallophyte	thicket	thimbleberry	thimbleweed	thistle	thoroughwort	thrift	throatwort	thyme	thyrsopteris	ti	tick-weed	tickseed	tickweed	tidytips	timothy	tipu	tithonia	titi	toadflax	toadshade	tobacco	toetoe	toitoi	tollon	tomatillo	tomato	tongue-flower	tongueflower	toothwort	torch	tornillo	totara	touch-me-not	toyon	tracheophyte	tread-softly	tree	treelet	trefoil	trifoliata	trillium	tritoma	trompillo	trumpet-wood	trumpets	trumpetwood	tuberose	tuckahoe	tulip	tumbleweed	tuna	tung	tupelo	turmeric	turnip	turreae	turtlehead	tutsan	twayblade	twinberry	twinflower	twistwood	umbellifer	umbrellawort	underbrush	undergrowth	undershrub	underwood	ursinia	valerian	vanda	vanilla	vase-fine	vegetable	vegetation	velvet-leaf	velvetleaf	velvetweed	verbena	verdolagas	vernonia	veronica	vervain	vetch	vetchling	vine	vinegarweed	vinifera	viola	violet	wahoo	wake-robin	waldmeister	wallflower	walnut	wampee	wandflower	waratah	wartweed	wartwort	wasabi	water-mint	water-shield	water-target	watercress	waterleaf	watermeal	watermelon	waterweed	wattle	waxberry	waxflower	waxmallow	waxwork	weed	weigela	weld	welwitschia	wheat	wheat-grass	wheatgrass	whin	whinberry	whitecup	whitethorn	whitlavia	whitlowwort	whortleberry	wickup	wicopy	wildflower	wilding	willow	willowherb	windflower	wineberry	wing-nut	wingstem	winterberry	wint
